# 📋 Menu

```
1. Insert Study Log
2. View Study Logs
3. Export Logs to CSV
4. Summary by Date
5. Summary by Subject
6. Exit
```

---

# 🚀 Compilation

Compile

```bash
javac StudyTracker.java
```

Run

```bash
java MarvellousStudyTracker
```

