# 📈 Advantages

- Simple and user-friendly interface
- Easy to maintain study history
- Generates useful summaries
- CSV export for external analysis
- Lightweight console application
- Modular object-oriented design

---

# ⚠️ Limitations

- Data is stored only during runtime (no persistent storage)
- Console-based interface
- Single-user application
- No editing or deleting of study logs
- No graphical analytics

